&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PRIVATE PATIENTS SERVICES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;BAND 2 – Healthcare assistants &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;37.5 HOURS PER WEEK&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Part Time Hours Negotiable&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Parkside Suite is a Private Patient Unit situated within Frimley Health NHS Foundation Trust. It offers high standards of care with 15 in-patient rooms. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;We are currently seeking highly motivated and enthusiastic healthcare assistants, who are looking for a stimulating and challenging environment to join our supportive and friendly team. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;You should enjoy working as part of a team and demonstrate excellent customer care and communication skills. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;We positively promote the opportunity of working with variety of clients and specialists whilst also enjoying the benefits of belonging to an acute NHS Foundation Trust. Our Trust prides itself on offering comprehensive staff development opportunities, a full induction programme with full support and training. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Working hours will be based on internal rotation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you have any queries please contact Senior Sister Louise Peasley on 01753 634550.&lt;/p&gt;
